86
00:05:39.991 --> 00:05:42.084
[truck backup alarm
beeping outside]

87
00:05:42.167 --> 00:05:43.608
Oh. damn it.

88
00:05:43.691 --> 00:05:45.170
Hey!

89
00:05:46.171 --> 00:05:47.608
Hey. buddy.

90
00:05:48.609 --> 00:05:50.005
