[cries out]

144
00:09:47.282 --> 00:09:49.066
[crunching]

145
00:09:50.764 --> 00:09:52.156
[whimpering]

146
00:09:56.726 --> 00:09:58.989
-[breathing heavily]
-[others groaning]

147
00:10:08.085 --> 00:10:09.826
[gun cocks]

148
00:10:18.922 --> 00:10:20.750
[elevator bell dings]

149
00:10:24.493 --> 00:10:26.060
[body thuds]

150
00:10:28.279 --> 00:10:30.503
Right. Straightforward snatch.

151
00:10:30.586 --> 00:10:33.898
Yeah. Until the Corsicans
showed up with Uzis.

152
00:10:33.981 --> 00:10:36.244
♪ ♪

153
00:10:39.551 --> 00:10:42.206
Wait. No. they had MP7s.

154
00:10:52.042 --> 00:10:53.827
-[explosion booms]
-[man yells]

155
00:10:54.871 --> 00:10:55.920
Corsicans. huh?

156
00:10:56.003 --> 00:10:58.531
With MP7s.

157
00:10:58.614 --> 00:11:00.228
Well. we always
suspected there might be

158
00:11:00.311 --> 00:11:02.448
another interested
party in the mix.

159
00:11:02.531 --> 00:11:04.402
Only one?

160
00:11:05.621 --> 00:11:08.019
[tires squealing]

161
00:11:08.102 --> 00:11:11.413
["100% Feminista" by MC Carol &
Karol Conká plays over stereo]

162
00:11:11.496 --> 00:11:13.328
[song continues with
lyrics in Portuguese]

163
00:11:13.411 --> 00:11:15.239
[tires squealing]

164
00:11:19.026 --> 00:11:20.723
[sighs]

165
00:11:24.422 --> 00:11:25.950
[electrical crackling]

166
00:11:26.033 --> 00:11:28.470
-[fierce grunting]
-["100% Feminista" continues]

167
00:11:30.515 --> 00:11:32.866
[grunting and groaning]

168
00:11:35.346 --> 00:11:36.395
[song stops]

169
00:11:36.478 --> 00:11:38.745
-Brazilians?
-HUTCH: Yeah.

170
00:11:38.828 --> 00:11:40.312
With machetes?

171
00:11:40.395 --> 00:11:41.487
The sharp kind.

172
00:11:41.570 --> 00:11:43.659
[song resumes]

173
00:11:49.883 --> 00:11:50.931
[song stops]

174
00:11:51.014 --> 00:11:52.193
Oh. my.

175
00:11:52.276 --> 00:11:53.542
Yeah.

176
00:11:53.625 --> 00:11:54.935
Oh. my.

177
00:11:55.018 --> 00:11:57.068
[tablet beeping]

178
00:11:57.151 --> 00:11:59.196
[trilling. beeping]

179
00:12:03.070 --> 00:12:04.815
Well. I'd say it was worth it.

180
00:12:04.898 --> 00:12:06.595
Because this checks out.

181
00:12:07.639 --> 00:12:10.730
Which brings you
800 grand closer.

182
00:12:13.254 --> 00:12:15.256
And how much more do I owe?

183
00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:18.302
30 million. give or take.

184
00:12:19.434 --> 00:12:20.696
[snaps fingers]

185
00:12:24.178 --> 00:12:26.789
